{"tid":1283872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我有嘢講】致 行政長官林鄭月娥邀請信","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T20:54:18.000Z","uid":51814,"like":276,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e785099531126fd22e69c3256c1140013b5179b7","tid":1283872,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"致 行政長官林鄭月娥邀請信<br />\n<br />\n回應特首於七一升旗禮酒會所說，特首已明白作為從政者，會不時儆醒自己去準確掌握民情，而在網絡群組已收集不少香港市民的意願，正在等候特首以開放包容的態度去耐心聆聽，相信能令政府工作更貼近民心民情民意。<br />\n<br />\n特首承諾的最基本一步，政府施政風格要更開放更包容，而聽取民意的工作，已經刻不容緩。現在正好有一個機會，可以與不同黨派、不同階層、不同背景的香港市民面對面接觸，聽取他們的意願，尤其是年青人的心聲，讓香港重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n由於我們只是一群自發的香港人，資源有限，只能於逢週日由香港電台舉辦的「城市論壇」節目中，與大眾討論發表意見，現我們誠邀特首親臨我們當中，展開與民同行的第一步。雖知特首公務繁忙，若特首應邀參與，我們香港人必會以真誠相對，敬候大駕光臨。<br />\n<br />\n7月7日中午12時正，維多利亞公園涼亭，城市論壇節目，We Connect！<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的市民敬上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/04/105404_d1f63a6a0ae035e7a035e98e3c90bf17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F04%2F105404_d1f63a6a0ae035e7a035e98e3c90bf17.jpg&h=94154e14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71c14ae747ffcf5b2368447077771cd8fa1b8d18","tid":1283872,"uid":119458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"上個post有巴打提出，可以講到我地係應邀出席，回應佢記者會話要聽民意<br />\n-<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"3c92e1dc3881ee7607fd9b1e5f47ee53080a393f","tid":1283872,"uid":51814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">7.7集會主題 : 林鄭特首聆聽大會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/QhaFdU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/QhaFdU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原post</span>"},{"pid":"636d073dd49f75e1e50b2bf8fed5edf86f3c4bd6","tid":1283872,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"快推"},{"pid":"f0a0e10056bc1fe1bdbe060900e19c3dcc6e9a7d","tid":1283872,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要搵律師 (背定律師電話)<br />\n我唔簽任何文件<br />\n我唔信任何警察<br />\n我要警誡記錄<br />\n我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所<br />\n我唔舒服要去醫院<br />\n我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你"},{"pid":"1c2b7ae566928e18110a4f69ef5400938cb1effa","tid":1283872,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"61c68ad3ea249b75d81d471adedbe011a8174ee2","tid":1283872,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P12kum-DSWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP12kum-DSWA&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=6d03fafc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P12kum-DSWA</a><br />\n<br />\n七一升旗禮酒會林鄭講話"},{"pid":"3515675ff6c618ed59470091e288ba80f428a097","tid":1283872,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />誠邀<br />\n<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"f3c8feb5408b6df57c348fc51423c58144dc004b","tid":1283872,"uid":34594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:53:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98a00b08eda2de15c6f50a7e7932a3792107c0cc","tid":1283872,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWe connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31067e283b9aaecfc14f0c674312a5f15c8f57fa","tid":1283872,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla